Class BufferPanel

ca.phon.app.log.BufferPanel
All Implemented Interfaces:
IExtendable, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
Direct Known Subclasses:
GitProgressBuffer
public class BufferPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements IExtendable
A panel showing a single LogBuffer with options for displaying the data in different formats. CSV data may be displayed in a table, while HTML data may be rendered inside a JEditorPane.
